        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-10-06 02:03:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(8 inline comments)\n\nI have pointed out a few minor white space issues. \n\nI am not an expert in this code path.  Is this a fast path area?  I see a global lock and I want to be sure we all understand that it is not a spot that can easily bottle neck.  \n\nCan you add to the comment of why the current code is incorrect and new locking is needed? I can't see MRP-206.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
