          "date": "2012-08-02 20:31:12.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-977 osc: incorrect round robin allocation",
        "message": "LU-977 osc: incorrect round robin allocation\n\nprotect round robin allocations with additional spinlock.\nMove object preallcoation into separate thread, avoiding the\nsituation when two threads start allocation from same index.\nFix up osc_precreate() return values.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-206\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Bruce Korb <bruce_korb@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <Andriy_Skulysh@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I31fa104383acdacba1f1c60ebf505d2c38cabcf7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
